          <p>This dashboard is populated by <b>NetFlow Optimizer</b> (NFO) Logic Module <b>“10267: AWS Top Traffic Monitor”</b> (syslogs with nfc_id=20267). This Module identifies AWS EC2 instances with the most traffic. It consolidates VPC Flow records over a period of time (Data Collection Interval) which all have the same combination of the following fields: Source IP address, Destination IP address, Source port number, Destination port number, Layer 3 protocol. This Module is packaged in <b>NFO “AWS VPC Flow Logs” Module Set</b>.</p>
          <p>Please either change the Time Range or make sure that this NFO Logic Module is enabled. See <a href="/app/netflow/configuration/" target="_blank">NSO Configuration</a> for more details.</p>
